      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. This example exhibits strong mid-range torque and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline, with recent VANOS solenoid replacement and valve clearance adjustments ensuring peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement plates to address known structural fatigue, paired with refreshed polyurethane bushings for sharpened suspension geometry. Power is delivered through a functional M-Variable limited-slip differential, providing exceptional traction during corner exit. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain remains robust with consistent oil analysis results and no signs of rod bearing wear. A technically sound platform for the purist driver.",
